statements: SELECT * FROM BuildingSpaces;
SELECT space_name, occupancy_status FROM BuildingSpaces WHERE occupancy_count > 10;
SELECT space_name, utilization_efficiency FROM BuildingSpaces ORDER BY utilization_efficiency DESC;
SELECT space_id, space_name FROM BuildingSpaces WHERE space_name LIKE 'Meeting%';
SELECT space_name, occupancy_count FROM BuildingSpaces WHERE utilization_efficiency < 0.5;
SELECT space_name, occupancy_status FROM BuildingSpaces WHERE occupancy_count > 50 ORDER BY space_name ASC
SELECT * FROM BuildingSpaces WHERE utilization_efficiency < 0.75 ORDER BY space_id DESC
SELECT space_name, occupancy_count, utilization_efficiency FROM BuildingSpaces WHERE occupancy_status = 'Occupied' ORDER BY occupancy_count DESC
SELECT space_id, space_name, utilization_efficiency FROM BuildingSpaces WHERE occupancy_count = 0 ORDER BY space_id ASC
SELECT space_id, utilization_efficiency FROM BuildingSpaces WHERE occupancy_status = 'Vacant' ORDER BY utilization_efficiency DESC
SELECT * FROM building_spaces;
SELECT space_name, occupancy_status FROM building_spaces WHERE occupancy_status = TRUE;
SELECT space_name, occupancy_capacity FROM building_spaces WHERE space_name LIKE 'Meeting%';
SELECT id, space_name, occupancy_status FROM building_spaces ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT space_name, occupancy_timestamp FROM building_spaces JOIN occupancy_log ON building_spaces.id = occupancy_log.space_id;
SELECT * FROM building_spaces WHERE occupancy_status = TRUE;
SELECT space_name, occupancy_capacity FROM building_spaces WHERE occupancy_capacity > 50 ORDER BY space_name ASC;
SELECT space_name, COUNT(*) AS total_occupancy FROM building_spaces WHERE occupancy_status = TRUE GROUP BY space_name;
SELECT space_name, occupancy_timestamp FROM building_spaces JOIN occupancy_log ON building_spaces.id = occupancy_log.space_id WHERE occupancy_status = TRUE ORDER BY occupancy_timestamp DESC;

SELECT space_name, occupancy_capacity, COUNT(*) AS total_occupancy FROM building_spaces WHERE occupancy_status = TRUE GROUP BY space_name, occupancy_capacity HAVING COUNT(*) > 1 ORDER BY total_occupancy DESC;
SELECT * FROM occupancy_patterns WHERE occupancy_status = TRUE;
SELECT room_name, occupancy_status FROM occupancy_patterns WHERE room_name = 'Office';
SELECT room_name, efficiency_score FROM utilization_efficiency ORDER BY efficiency_score DESC;
SELECT space_name, location, capacity FROM green_building_spaces WHERE capacity > 50;
SELECT * FROM occupancy_patterns WHERE occupancy_status = FALSE;
SELECT * FROM occupancy_patterns WHERE occupancy_status = TRUE
SELECT room_name FROM occupancy_patterns WHERE id = 3
SELECT space_name, location FROM green_building_spaces ORDER BY space_name DESC
SELECT room_name, efficiency_score FROM utilization_efficiency WHERE efficiency_score > 80 ORDER BY efficiency_score DESC
SELECT * FROM green_building_spaces WHERE capacity >= 50
SELECT * FROM occupancy_data;
SELECT space_id, occupancy_count FROM occupancy_data WHERE occupancy_count > 50;
SELECT building_name, address FROM building_details;
SELECT space_name, floor_number, building_id FROM space_details WHERE building_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT * FROM floor_details ORDER BY floor_number DESC;
SELECT * FROM occupancy_data WHERE occupancy_count > 50 ORDER BY occupancy_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT space_id, occupancy_count FROM occupancy_data WHERE occupancy_timestamp < '2022-01-01' AND occupancy_count BETWEEN 20 AND 30;

SELECT od.space_id, sd.space_name, bd.building_name FROM occupancy_data od JOIN space_details sd ON od.space_id = sd.space_id JOIN building_details bd ON sd.building_id = bd.building_id WHERE bd.building_name = 'Office Building A';
SELECT space_id, COUNT(*) AS occupancy_records FROM occupancy_data GROUP BY space_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 5 ORDER BY occupancy_records DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT bd.building_name, COUNT(*) AS total_spaces FROM building_details bd JOIN space_details sd ON bd.building_id = sd.building_id JOIN occupancy_data od ON sd.space_id = od.space_id GROUP BY bd.building_name ORDER BY total_spaces DESC;
SELECT * FROM building_spaces;
SELECT space_name, area_size FROM building_spaces WHERE floor_number = 3;
SELECT space_name, occupancy_status FROM building_spaces WHERE area_size > 100 AND occupancy_status = TRUE;
SELECT * FROM occupancy_logs ORDER BY occupancy_start DESC;
SELECT space_id, electricity_usage, water_usage, heating_usage FROM energy_consumption WHERE electricity_usage > 100 OR water_usage > 50;
SELECT * FROM building_spaces WHERE floor_number > 5 ORDER BY space_name DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT space_name, area_size FROM building_spaces WHERE occupancy_status = TRUE AND floor_number = 3;

SELECT space_name, occupancy_status, observation_date FROM building_spaces JOIN occupancy_patterns ON building_spaces.id = occupancy_patterns.space_id WHERE observation_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-04-30';

SELECT space_name, electricity_usage, water_usage, heating_usage FROM building_spaces JOIN energy_consumption ON building_spaces.id = energy_consumption.space_id WHERE electricity_usage > 1000 OR water_usage > 500 OR heating_usage > 300;
SELECT pattern_id, pattern_description, evaluation_date FROM occupancy_patterns JOIN efficiency_metrics ON occupancy_patterns.space_id = efficiency_metrics.space_id WHERE efficiency_score > 0.8;
